InventoryForecastVariance is a BusinessTask
    owned by ic

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for SupplyManagementProcessor, Buyer, InventoryManager, PurchasingManager, WarehouseClerk, ApplicationAdministrator, SupplyManagementViewer, Inventory
                report name is "ForecastVariance"
                Description
                    View report that compares actual usage quantities to item forecast quantities.
            Reports
                InventoryForecastVarianceReport

    Parameters
        Company                 is an InventoryCompany
        Location                is an InventoryLocation
        RptGroup                is an InventoryReportGroup
        FrCurrPeriod            is Numeric size 2
        FrForecastYear          is Numeric size 4
        ToCurrPeriod            is Numeric size 2
        ToForecastYear          is Numeric size 4
        CutoffPct               is Decimal size 4.1
        ForecastNbr             is Numeric size 4
        IssueFlag               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        TransferFlag            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        AdjustmentFlag          is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
        InvenMajcl              is a MajorInventoryClass
        InvenMincl              is a MinorInventoryClass

	Parameter Rules
		Company
			required
		IssueFlag
			initial value is "N"
			default to "N"
		TransferFlag
			initial value is "N"
			default to "N"
		AdjustmentFlag
			initial value is "N"
			default to "N"

    Actions
        InventoryForecastVariance is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
